            />
          </svg>
          View Code on GitHub
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Text content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg">

        <p>
          <strong>Uniswap V2 Sniperbot</strong> is an automated trading bot designed
          to buy tokens immediately after they are listed on Uniswap V2.
          The bot allows fine-grained control over entry price, trade size,
          stop loss and execution strategy.
        </p>

        <h2>Use Case</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Monitoring new pair creation on Uniswap V2</li>
          <li>Instant buy at listing time</li>
          <li>Automated risk management</li>
          <li>Hands-off execution during token launches</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Core Features</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Real-time detection of newly deployed Uniswap V2 pairs</li>
          <li>Configurable buy price and amount</li>
          <li>Stop loss and take profit logic</li>
          <li>Gas price and slippage control</li>
          <li>Transaction retry and failure handling</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Architecture</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Event-driven architecture</li>
          <li>Direct interaction with Uniswap V2 smart contracts</li>
          <li>WebSocket-based blockchain listeners</li>
          <li>Config-driven strategy parameters</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Node.js</li>
          <li>ethers.js</li>
          <li>Web3 APIs</li>
          <li>Uniswap V2 contracts</li>
          <li>Ethereum JSON-RPC</li>
        </ul>

      </div>

    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>